Class AbstractEmitter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.snowplowanalytics.snowplow.tracker.emitter.AbstractEmitter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Emitter
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BatchEmitter, SimpleEmitter

    public abstract class AbstractEmitter
extends java.lang.Object
implements Emitter
    AbstractEmitter class which contains common elements to the emitters wrapped in a builder format. Note that SimpleEmitter has been deprecated.
